**🔮 Welcome to the Miracle Bot! 🔮**
  
This bot is used for coordinating the community of your discord server and helping the community to complete bounties of a thing you're building. It's very simple!

  **🔮 Please use these commands:**
  **/welcome** - Check out what the bot can do 👀
  **/setup** - Setup this bot after adding it to the server 🖲
  **/new_bounty** - Add new bounty 🎁
  **/send_solution** - Send a bounty solution 📜
  **/approve_solution** - Approve a bounty solution 👍

This is still an alpha version of the Miracle Bot. Please, send Desputes & Bugs & Feedback to https://twitter.com/kirillzzy.
  
WAGMI 😈
Pinned a message.
😇 Creating new bounty! What's the bounty name?
Write Hyperscale Twitter Thread
📜 What is the description?

Write about what Hyperscale is doing, what you think of it, and/or how you're involved.

Resources for developing a deep understanding:
- https://hyperscalefund.notion.site/Welcome-to-Hyperscale-12a06b6fe3c14b9c92db9a5a3298b862
- https://hyperscalefund.notion.site/DAO-Race-2c22ac7105264666b52426f595f056a5
- https://discord.com/channels/916751469678579784/916797646071541811/923125150864523264

Example:
- https://twitter.com/aletherx/status/1469099308762943496
- https://twitter.com/m1guelpf/status/1468396389184913409
- https://twitter.com/HyperscaleFund/status/1468391440283684868

embeds.title: Welcome to Hyperscale
embeds.description: The Hyperscale vision is to be the most effective capital allocator in the world, at all stages, and at extreme scale. We make creating, funding, and investing in DAOs easier than any other platform. Hyperscale is a fund that allocates not only monetary resources but human resources. An ecosystem fund for the new economy.

embeds.title: DAO Race
embeds.description: Learn from other DAOs, make progress, and earn funding.

Was looking to get involved in an early web3/DAO project for a while. Then saw yesterday @sama's tweet on @HyperscaleFund. 

Immediately realised the potential and started building. 

But to me, the edge of Hyperscale is not that it's a DAO, invests in web3 or even its speed. 👇

✨ It's been super fun to help build @HyperscaleFund over the past two days.

With @ConstitutionDAO we showed the world that ideas can iterate much much faster in web3, and now HyperscaleDAO wants to match that speed to fund them.

https://t.co/mxIJHv18Tb

🚀 Announcing HyperscaleDAO, ultra-fast funding for web3 projects.

We want to be the most effective capital allocator in the world, allowing anyone with an idea to submit an application, and providing funding in less than a week.

Here's how you can get started 👇
